# Project Methodology

The project followed a structured data analytics workflow.

## 1. Data Collection

Loan application data was obtained from the provided lending dataset.

## 2. Data Cleaning

The dataset was inspected for:

- Missing values
- Duplicate records
- Inconsistent formatting
- Invalid values

Cleaning activities included:

- Standardizing text values
- Replacing missing values
- Creating calculated categories
- Validating numeric fields

## 3. Data Analysis

Exploratory analysis focused on identifying patterns related to loan defaults.

Key variables included:

- Loan Grade
- Annual Income
- Debt-to-Income Ratio
- Employment Length
- Interest Rate

## 4. Dashboard Development

Power BI was used to develop an interactive dashboard featuring:

- KPI Cards
- Charts
- Slicers
- Navigation Buttons
- Business Insights

## 5. Reporting

Insights were documented together with business recommendations to support decision-making.
